      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d072n1-ptr" id="PJA04d072n1">1</a>
      
   <p>Warren to <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-04-02-0029" class="document">30 March</a> (above).</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d072n2-ptr" id="PJA04d072n2">2</a>
      
   <p><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Paradise Lost</span>, Book 5, line 601.</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d072n3-ptr" id="PJA04d072n3">3</a>
      
   <p>Elias Wrixon from England, whom Samuel Adams, as a member of a congressional committee for the purpose, recommended be appointed adjutant general in Canada at the rank of brigadier general. <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> recalled years later that the appointment of Wrixon had been a serious source of controversy in the congress (Richard Smiths Diary, in <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Edmund C. Burnett, ed., &lt;i&gt;Letters of Members of the Continental Congress&lt;/i&gt;, Washington, 19211936; 8 vols. ]">Burnett, ed., <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Letters of Members</span></span>, 1:400, 407408; <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Diary and Autobiography of John Adams&lt;/i&gt;, ed. L. H. Butterfield and others, Cambridge, 1961; 4 vols. ]">JA, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Diary and Autobiography</span></span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-01-03-02-0016-0114" class="document">3:382</a>). Gates was promoted to major general on 16 May (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Worthington C. Ford and others, eds., &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Continental Congress&lt;/i&gt;, 17741789, Washington, 19041937; 34 vols. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">JCC</span></span>, 4:359).</p>

